  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Tactical Zone, an exciting cooperative third-person shooter that will give you adrenaline and unforgettable moments on the battlefield! Gather a team of four players and enter the battle, where your cohesion and tactical skills will be the key to victory.<br><br>In Tactical Zone you will face endless waves of enemies on various maps. Your task is to hold out as long as possible, deflecting the onslaught of enemy forces. <br><br>Are you ready to take on the challenge and prove your skill on the battlefield? Join Tactical Zone and become a legend in the world of tactical shooters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tactical third-person battles.<br></li><li>Team gameplay and cooperative operations.<br></li><li>Endless waves.<br></li><li>Interesting maps and combat atmosphere.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCORD</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Join our Discord community to participate in game development, stay up to date with the latest news, and offer your ideas and help find bugs!<br></li></ul>.",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to Tactical Zone, an exciting cooperative third-person shooter that will give you adrenaline and unforgettable moments on the battlefield! Gather a team of four players and enter the battle, where your cohesion and tactical skills will be the key to victory.<br><br>In Tactical Zone you will face endless waves of enemies on various maps. Your task is to hold out as long as possible, deflecting the onslaught of enemy forces. <br><br>Are you ready to take on the challenge and prove your skill on the battlefield? Join Tactical Zone and become a legend in the world of tactical shooters!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Tactical third-person battles.<br></li><li>Team gameplay and cooperative operations.<br></li><li>Endless waves.<br></li><li>Interesting maps and combat atmosphere.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DISCORD</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Join our Discord community to participate in game development, stay up to date with the latest news, and offer your ideas and help find bugs!<br></li></ul>.",
